From 123e855d2da3bd276e5034c97127e827aaad1c2e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Vivek Chettri <vchettri@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Fri, 11 Jul 2025 00:33:02 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] UPSTREAM:PROTOCOL:CP:wifi:ath12k: Add support for handling
 QoS Management requests

Add support in ath12k to handle QoS Management (QM) configuration
requests forwarded from mac80211. This enables the driver to interpret
and respond to user-space QoS Management requests based on type
(Add, Del, Update) and protocol (e.g., SCS or other vendor-specific QM
protocols).

The implementation allows the driver to access QM descriptors, apply
protocol-specific logic, and return per-descriptor status, enabling
fine-grained control and feedback for QoS operations.

As part of the SCS request handling, add/delete/update SCS related data
into the peer QoS context.

Patch-dependency:
0415-0001-UPSTREAM-CP-wifi-ath12k-Add-APIs-to-configure-QoS-pa.patch
0415-0002-UPSTREAM-CP-wifi-ath12k-Enable-QoS-support-in-the-Fi.patch
0415-0003-UPSTREAM-DP-wifi-ath12k-Add-support-for-QoS-Datapath.patch
